data.title: Scanfjord
data.text:
Scanfjord - The leading producer of

cultivated mussels in Sweden.

The cultivation of blue mussels and sales of several

types of mussels, are the company's core business.

Sales office is located in Gothenburg and

the production taking place in Moll√∂sund.

The activity includes development and

sales of cultivaiting systems to other farmers in

Sweden and other Nordic countries.

Scanfjord also offers services in form of starting up,

harvest and maintenance services for buyers

of cultivating systems..
